snippet.title: Doom 64 - N64 - Map01
snippet.description:
Here's a 100% runthrough of Doom 64 Map01: Staging Area. Doom 64 is a completely new Doom that was released for the Nintendo 64.

I know I never played through all of Hectic. Maybe someday I'll do a video of it. But since it's the hardest level, and it starts you right back at the beginning of Staging Area again, I figured I'd just go onto Map02, The Terraformer.

Lastly, a shameless plug. :P Check out my site at http://doomdepot.doom2.net/ for the Doom 64 Total Conversion, and all the Doom music you can possibly want.
